"\n"
"            Agriculture plays a critical role in India's economic "
"development and is the backbone of our agrarian economy.\n"
"            By using machine learning to recommend crops, we can increase"
" agricultural productivity and sustainability.\n"
"            Our system analyzes soil composition (Nitrogen, Phosphorus, "
